💻 I’m actively building a portfolio to showcase my learning and projects. Right now, I offer free services like:

docs.title: 💼 Services
docs.text: I offer a range of services to help you with your tech and content needs. My goal is to provide valuable solutions while gaining hands-on experience in the process.

docs.title: 1. PDF to Markdown Conversion
docs.text: • Are your PDF documents cluttered with unformatted content? I can convert your PDF notes to Markdown format, making them clean, easy to read, and ready for digital use.

docs.title: 2. MkDocs Website Creation
docs.text: • Want a website to showcase your portfolio, blog, or documentation? I specialize in building MkDocs-based websites that are clean, user-friendly, and easy to maintain. Whether you're a developer, researcher, or blogger, I’ll bring your website vision to life.

docs.title: 3. Consultation & Support in AI and Data Science (Coming Soon)
docs.text: • 🚀 I am in the process of offering AI and Data Science services, including data analysis, machine learning models, and data visualization. As I develop my expertise, I’ll provide more advanced services for your AI and Data Science needs.

docs.title: 💡 Why Choose Me?
docs.text:
• I’m a passionate learner who is constantly improving my skills.
  • Affordable pricing with reasonable charges tailored to your needs.
  • Discounts for students available.
  • For a limited time, I am offering free services to build my portfolio and gain practical experience.
  • My focus is always on delivering high-quality results while providing great customer support.

📩 If you're interested in any of my services, feel free to reach out! You can find my contact details in the Contact section.

I'm excited to collaborate and help you with your projects.
